00:45:12.299 --> 00:45:19.519
and all right, and after they got married,
both of them started living together. And

00:45:19.519 --> 00:45:27.339
I can't understand. Before marriage, it never
entered into their head. After marriage, why

00:45:27.339 --> 00:45:29.680
this has entered into their head?

00:45:29.680 --> 00:45:35.339
'Mother, we don't know what to do now.' You
see, that, that French boy is fed up, he said,

00:45:35.339 --> 00:45:40.079
' I have nothing to do with this but for this
Indian girl, what to do, what am I to tell

00:45:40.079 --> 00:45:44.650
her?' Because for her, he's her husband. Because
